// AUTO-GENERATED — Rubik (Google Fonts, SIL OFL 1.1) embedded as base64 so the
// react-pdf font travels inside the Vercel serverless bundle with no
// filesystem / output-file-tracing dependency (same reason the company logo
// is embedded as a data-URI in load-data.ts).
//
// Built from the official variable Rubik (google/fonts ofl/rubik), instanced
// to static weights with fontTools and subset to Latin-1 + General
